* Configure\nManaged Storage
** Recommended: specify MANAGED LOCATION
***_ Points to ADLS Gen2 container
***_ Requires CREATE MANAGED STORAGE privilege
** Physical data isolation
***_ Data files per catalog path
***_ Safe deletion after 8-day retention
** Compliance requirements
***_ Specific storage accounts or regions
***_ Regulatory obligation support
** Without catalog storage
***_ Falls back to metastore default
***_ Must specify if no metastore default
** SQL syntax
***_ CREATE CATALOG ... MANAGED LOCATION '...'
@endmindmap
